    "attributes": {
        "action": "Exempt vehicles 25 years and over from vehicle road tax",
        "additional_details": "Because I think for a vehicle to be forty years old to eligible for free road tax and MOT is too long. Many modern vehicles may not last over 25 years.",
        "background": "I would like Government to reconsider allowing no road duty on vehicles 25 and over. It would help keep many more classic British cars on the road.",
